    <title type="html"><![CDATA[[AWS]媽~~我會架了，運用CloudFormation建立雲端系統]]></title>
    <link href="http://blog.sammylin.tw/aws-e5-aa-bd-e6-88-91-e6-9c-83-e6-9e-b6-e4-ba-86-ef-bc-8c-e9-81-8b-e7-94-a8cloudformation-e5-bb-ba-e7-ab-8b-e9-9b-b2-e7-ab-af-e7-b3-bb-e7-b5-b1/"/>
    <updated>2011-06-22T00:00:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://blog.sammylin.tw/aws-e5-aa-bd-e6-88-91-e6-9c-83-e6-9e-b6-e4-ba-86-ef-bc-8c-e9-81-8b-e7-94-a8cloudformation-e5-bb-ba-e7-ab-8b-e9-9b-b2-e7-ab-af-e7-b3-bb-e7-b5-b1</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><p> 可能有人不知道什麼是EC2,S3…等等等的，什麼都不知道也不會用，但是你想要用，那你一定要看這一篇，讓你幾個動作就可以完成所有的作業程序，包含建立EC2,S3,Elastic Load Balancer…等等的。看到下圖：我們只要把Template指令丟到CloudFormation裡面，由CloudFormation去執行以下的動作進行建置，我們就可以把一個系統建立起來不論你會不會使用API，都可以如此的方便快速又有效(這個時代講求效率呀~)</p> <img alt="" src="http://media.amazonwebservices.com/blog/cloudformation_1.png" />  <p>圖片來源：<a href="http://aws.typepad.com/aws/2011/02/cloudformation-create-your-aws-stack-from-a-recipe.html">http://aws.typepad.com/aws/2011/02/cloudformation-create-your-aws-stack-from-a-recipe.html</a></p><!--more--><p>我們一如往常的介紹用圖片來介紹怎麼使用(有誰可以教一下怎麼用螢幕錄影~又可以放大縮小的也可以貼註解的軟體阿)</p>  <h3>建立CloudFormation</h3>  <p><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image57.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb55.png" width="544" height="286" /></a></p>  <p><a href="https://console.aws.amazon.com/cloudformation/home?region=ap-northeast-1">https://console.aws.amazon.com/cloudformation/home?region=ap-northeast-1</a></p>  <p><font color="#0000ff">1.建立一個新的程序(Creat New Stack)</font></p>  <p><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image58.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb56.png" width="167" height="32" /></a></p>  <p><font color="#0000ff">2.Create Stack</font></p>  <p><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image59.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb57.png" width="544" height="420" /></a></p>  <p><font color="#ff0000">Stack Name</font>-程序的名稱(自已好記就好)    <br /><font color="#ff0000">Stack Template Source</font> -程序範本來源    <br />(可以用樣品的範本、或是自已做一個範本上傳、也可以貼範本的網址上去)</p>  <table border="2" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="540"><tbody>     <tr>       <td valign="top" width="540">Amazon 提供Stack Template：<a href="http://aws.amazon.com/cloudformation/aws-cloudformation-templates/">http://aws.amazon.com/cloudformation/aws-cloudformation-templates/</a></td>     </tr>   </tbody></table>  <p>其實範本就是長樣子</p>  <p><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image60.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb58.png" width="544" height="415" /></a></p>  <p>如果有興趣的人可以自已寫一個範本，其實是很方便的，他的語言也是很簡單易懂的。這邊就不多做介紹了。</p>  <p><font color="#0000ff">3.設定(其實這個設定是範本裡面預留使用者可以自已輸入的地方，在範本也是可以設定的)</font></p>  <p><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image61.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb59.png" width="544" height="472" /></a></p>  <p><font color="#0000ff">4.啥~預覽了~~真的不用再設定了嗎？…沒有錯xd</font><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image62.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb60.png" width="544" height="470" /></a></p>  <p><font color="#0000ff">5.接下來可以泡杯咖啡等著建立完成吧。</font><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image63.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb61.png" width="544" height="262" /></a></p>  <p><font color="#0000ff">6.約花了20分鐘建立完成</font></p>  <p><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image64.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb62.png" width="544" height="281" /></a></p>  <p><font color="#0000ff">7.到Outputs就可以知道你wordpress的網址</font><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image65.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb63.png" width="544" height="156" /></a></p>  <p><font color="#0000ff">8.完成</font></p>  <p><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image66.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb64.png" width="544" height="379" /></a></p>  <p><font color="#0000ff">9.架設完畢~可以寫Blog了！~~~</font><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image67.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb65.png" width="544" height="306" /></a></p>  <p>&#160;</p>  <p>我們看看他講我們建立了什麼！</p>  <p>CloudWatch<a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image68.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb66.png" width="544" height="278" /></a></p>  <p>RDS<a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image69.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb67.png" width="544" height="296" /></a></p>  <p>SNS<a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image70.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb68.png" width="544" height="295" /></a></p>  <p>EC2   <br /><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image71.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb69.png" width="544" height="283" /></a></p>  <p>Load Balancers   <br /><a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image72.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb70.png" width="544" height="283" /></a></p>  <p>Security Groups<a href="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image73.png"><img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb71.png" width="544" height="283" /></a></p>  <p>AutoScaling(連這個都有XD)<img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://blog-img.igotcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/image_thumb72.png" width="544" height="282" /></p>  <p>&#160;</p>  <p>看來以後都不用API啦~~把範本寫好用API來執行那不就大功告成了(哈哈~~~)</p>  <table border="2" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="540"><tbody>     <tr>       <td valign="top" width="540"><font size="2">相關資訊：           <br />AWS CloudFormation 範本：            <br /></font><a href="http://aws.amazon.com/cloudformation/aws-cloudformation-templates/"><font size="2">http://aws.amazon.com/cloudformation/aws-cloudformation-templates/</font></a>          <br /><font size="2">AWS Blog 介紹CloudFormation：           <br /></font><a href="http://aws.typepad.com/aws/2011/02/cloudformation-create-your-aws-stack-from-a-recipe.html"><font size="2">http://aws.typepad.com/aws/2011/02/cloudformation-create-your-aws-stack-from-a-recipe.html</font></a>          <br /><font size="2">AWS CloudFromation官方介紹：           <br /></font><a href="http://aws.amazon.com/cloudformation/"><font size="2">http://aws.amazon.com/cloudformation/</font></a>          <br />          <br /></td>     </tr>   </tbody></table></p>

